#!/usr/bin/env rad
---
Runs tests and dump tests for CI. Exits with proper codes.
Dedicated CI script - independent from dev script.
---

print("🧪 Running Go tests...")
$`go test ./core/testing ./rts`

print("🔍 Running dump tests...")
$`cd ./rts/test/dumps && ./test_dumps.rad`

print(green("✅ All tests passed!"))